ENTRY            D8115   20260202   20260508   20260508       D151
SUBENT        D8115001   20260202   20260508   20260508       D151
BIB                 10         21
TITLE      Study of the 7Li(d,t)6Li reaction at the energy of
           14.5 MeV
AUTHOR     (N.Burtebayev, Zh.K.Kerimkulov, Maulen Nassurlla,
            J.T.Burtebayeva, Marzhan Nassurlla, S.B.Sakuta,
            T.Suzuki, K.Rusek, A.Trzcinska, M.Wolinska-Cichocka)
INSTITUTE  (4KASKAZ,4KASAFU,4RUSKUR,2JPNSUU,3POLWWA)
REFERENCE  (J,APP/B,50,703,2019)
FACILITY   (ISOCY,4KASKAZ) U-150M
SAMPLE     (3-LI-7,ENR=0.9)
           0.4 mg/cm2 thick sample manufactured by thermal
            evaporation of lithium on a thin alundum (Al2O3) film
            (30 mg/cm2) in vacuum.
           After deposition, the target was transferred to a
            scattering chamber without breaking the vacuum.)
METHOD     (EDE)
DETECTOR   (TELES,SI,SI) dE E telescope of two silicon counters
            with thicknesses of 30,100 microns (dE detector) and
            2 mm (E detector)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Total uncertainty
HISTORY    (20260129C) Sanira Turganova
           (20260129R) Received by e-mail from Maulen Nassurlla
ENDBIB              21
COMMON               1          3
EN
MEV
 14.5
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           28
SUBENT        D8115002   20260202   20260508   20260508       D151
BIB                  2          2
REACTION   (3-LI-7(D,EL)3-LI-7,,DA)
STATUS     (TABLE,,N.Burtebayev+,J,APP/B,50,703,2019) Fig.3
ENDBIB               2
